  "title": "瞑想で目を閉じる必要はない",
  "created": 1672199277,
  "updated": 1672199277,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63abbc6dadea52001db0eb1f",
      "text": "瞑想で目を閉じる必要はない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f6e",
      "text": "from [独断的瞑想解説]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f6f",
      "text": "瞑想で目を閉じる必要はない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f70",
      "text": "Q: 目を閉じますか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f71",
      "text": "　A: 基本閉じないですね[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f72",
      "text": "　　仏教方面で名前がついてたはず",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f73",
      "text": "　　　「[半眼]」か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f74",
      "text": "　　　>仏像の眼（まなこ）は、見開くでもなく閉じてもいない、いわゆる「半眼」の眼差しです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f75",
      "text": "　　　https://mjj.or.jp/message/第66回%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C半眼の眼差し%E3%80%8D",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f76",
      "text": "　　歩く時に目を閉じたら危ない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f77",
      "text": "　　　今気づいたけども、今の僕にとって散歩が瞑想の位置を占めてるんだなぁ[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f78",
      "text": "　　蝋燭とか焚き火とかを見つめるやり方もよくある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f79",
      "text": "　　　[一点注視法]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f7a",
      "text": "　　　[護摩]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f7b",
      "text": "　　　[トラタカ瞑想]って言葉もあるみたいね、今知った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f7c",
      "text": "　　「閉じてはいけない」ってわけでもないのでどっちでも好きにしたらいいと思いますけど「閉じるべきだ」という主張には根拠がない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f7d",
      "text": "　　　閉じなくても感情が揺さぶられないような環境に行くことがまず優先",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672199277,
      "updated": 1672199277
    },
    {
      "id": "63abbc6daff09e0000fd7f7e",
